Throughout the build, deploy, and run phases of the development lifecycle, Prisma Cloud enables security teams to scale securely, and DevOps to deploy fearlessly.

Prisma Cloud for VMware Tanzu lets organizations continuously scan droplets in their blobstores for vulnerabilities.
The Prisma Cloud Intelligence Stream sources vulnerability data from commercial vendors, 30+ upstream projects, and proprietary research.
The Prisma Cloud scanner can be integrated directly into your CI pipeline to pass or fail builds based on policy.
Scan report data is available in open formats, including CSV and JSON. The comprehensive API makes it easy to integrate Prisma Cloud data into larger central dashboards.


## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

Prisma Cloud for VMware Tanzu lets you:

* Secure your apps at runtime with Prisma Cloud runtime defense.
* Gain visibility into the containers and hosts in your environment, their vulnerabilities and compliance issues.
* Continuously scan droplets in your blobstores for vulnerabilities.
* Continuously scan the images in your registries for vulnerabilities and compliance issues.
* Review and share scan reports across the team (Developers, DevOps, and Security).
* Raise alerts and route them to the right party when the scanner finds issues that violate policy (email, Slack, JIRA, and more).
* Integrate scanning into your CI/CD pipeline with the command line scanner. Pass or fail builds based on policy.
* Assess risk and pinpoint specific vulnerabilities in your environment with the Vulnerability Explorer.
* Retrieve scan report data via the comprehensive API for deep integration with other tools, dashboards, and processes.


